"If people voted for us, it doesn't mean they're stupid to vote for us if they don't see anything," said Blăjuț, who appreciated that the main reason why the electorate is no longer interested in politics is the hypocrisy of the elected.
A colleague from Tătăraşi said he's not getting his money and he has to ride the bus.
Let's not be hypocritical.
It's not a small amount of money.
Sometimes I'm ashamed to pick up the money from the locker.
